<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,1160,1979]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1340,1367]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Description.</emphasis>
Colonies from 
<quantity box="[520,650,1341,1367]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="0.7" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="10.0" valueMax="13.0" valueMin="7.0">7 to 13 mm</quantity>
high, monosiphonic, arising from a creeping hydrorhiza. Exoskeleton with visible layer corresponding to perisarc. Perisarc of hydrocaulus thick basally and thinner distally (1.0– 
<quantity box="[1355,1436,1377,1403]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.8" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="9.8">9.8 µm</quantity>
wide). Basal part of hydrocaulus without hydrothecae and hydrocladia; remainder of hydrocaulus longer (~ 
<quantity box="[1370,1437,1413,1439]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="9.0">9 mm</quantity>
long), regularly divided into internodes by straight nodes, with thecate and athecate internodes. Athecate internodes 
<quantity box="[151,335,1484,1511]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.678" metricValueMax="2.953" metricValueMin="2.403" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="267.8" valueMax="295.3" valueMin="240.3">240.3–295.3 µm</quantity>
long, with one median nematotheca and two nematothecae on either side of stem; thecate segments 317.7–340.0 µm long, each with one proximal nematotheca, one hydrotheca, two nematothecae lateral to hydrotheca, one median distal nematotheca, and two distal lateral nematothecae. Hydrocladia with two to six hydrothecae, unbranched, 
<quantity box="[298,414,1593,1619]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.2" metricValueMax="3.4" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="2.2" valueMax="3.4" valueMin="1.0">1–3.4 mm</quantity>
long, directed outwards at an angle of 30–40° from axis of hydrocaulus, with a series of one short athecate internode with no nematothecae, one athecate internode with two median nematothecae and one thecate internode with one proximal nematotheca, a distal hydrotheca, and two lateral nematothecae. All nematothecae bithalamic. Hydrothecae 136.0– 
<quantity box="[589,696,1701,1727]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.913" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="191.3">191.3 µm</quantity>
deep, cup-shaped, axis oblique to that of internode, margin entire, aperture circular, diameter 
<quantity box="[451,638,1736,1763]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3875" metricValueMax="1.5419999999999998" metricValueMin="1.233" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="138.75" valueMax="154.2" valueMin="123.3">123.3–154.2 µm</quantity>
. Gonotheca clavate, 
<quantity box="[868,1052,1736,1763]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.108" metricValueMax="6.254" metricValueMin="5.962" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="610.8" valueMax="625.4" valueMin="596.2">596.2–625.4 µm</quantity>
long, 189.0– 
<quantity box="[1199,1305,1737,1763]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9469999999999998" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="194.7">194.7 µm</quantity>
wide, aperture 
<quantity box="[202,310,1772,1799]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.451" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="145.1">145.1 µm</quantity>
wide; with two-segmented pedicel, arising from the base of hydrotheca on hydrocladia; exoskeleton corresponding to thin perisarc (2.0– 
<quantity box="[552,632,1809,1835]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.8" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="3.8">3.8 µm</quantity>
wide); base of gonotheca with two nematothecae.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,1160,1979]" box="[199,1129,1845,1872]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
Nematocysts (length x diam.). Microbasic mastigophores (8.2–10.0 x 
<quantity box="[983,1116,1845,1871]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" metricValueMax="4.4" metricValueMin="3.6" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="4.0" valueMax="4.4" valueMin="3.6">3.6–4.4 µm</quantity>
).
</paragraph>
